column2: ggplot(data, aes(x = serum_sodium)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 1, colour =  "white", fill = "slateblue", alpha = 0.7) + labs(title = "Histogram of Sodium in Blood") + geom_density(eval(bquote(aes(y=..count..))),colour="black") + geom_vline(xintercept = 135, linetype = "dashed") + geom_vline(xintercept = 145, linetype = "dashed")
